1
00:01:20,860 --> 00:01:26,730
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:29,720
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,560
Mother.

4
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,370
Mother, what's the matter?

5
00:01:36,370 --> 00:01:38,500
Why did you call me here in such a hurry?

6
00:01:39,789 --> 00:01:40,920
You may leave first.

7
00:01:41,789 --> 00:01:42,479
Yes.

8
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,350
Yesterday,

9
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:54,840
Zhao came to me,

10
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,840
saying the Ji family

11
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,180
wants back those 20,000 taels of silver.

12
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,070
What 20,000 taels of silver?

13
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:04,470
Those 20,000 taels.

14
00:02:05,770 --> 00:02:08,960
-15 years ago...
-20 years ago.

15
00:02:09,430 --> 00:02:10,470
Right, right.

16
00:02:10,889 --> 00:02:12,090
I completely forgot.

17
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,840
But why would the Ji family

18
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,520
suddenly remember this now?

19
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,310
I guess

20
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:21,280
someone close to Ji Han told them.

21
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,140
What did Zhao say?

22
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,360
I played dumb

23
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,490
and said I didn't remember.

24
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:30,190
But there was an IOU back then.

25
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,150
It's been 20 years now.

26
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,290
I was just hoping

27
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:36,370
they wouldn't be able to find the IOU.

28
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:42,840
This matter must not be made public.

29
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,180
The position of
Vice Minister of Personnel is vacant,

30
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:48,310
and I'm currently maneuvering for it.

31
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,890
At this critical juncture,

32
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,090
we can't afford any complications.

33
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:53,630
Of course I know that.

34
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,190
But that Zhao

35
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,450
is clearly not someone to be trifled with.

36
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,160
The Yao family is coming soon

37
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,910
to check Lian's dowry list.

38
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:07,910
As for you,

39
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,080
think carefully.

40
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:12,710
This matter

41
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,960
is a hidden danger after all.

42
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:26,840
Mother.

43
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,060
Mother.

44
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,000
This

45
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,680
is Lian's dowry list.

46
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,190
Let me read it to you

47
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:36,280
so you can see if it's appropriate.

48
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,840
Go ahead, I'm listening.

49
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:42,680
Old Madam,

50
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,130
Madam Yao is at the door.

51
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:45,800
Please invite her in quickly.

52
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,190
Yes.

53
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,000
People from the Yao family are here.

54
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,470
This marriage

55
00:03:52,490 --> 00:03:53,520
is settled.

56
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,130
That's what he said?

57
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:00,970
Where is he?

58
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,870
I was afraid he might run
into someone from the Yao family,

59
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,560
so I led him to Zhao's courtyard.

60
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,890
You did the right thing.

61
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,470
Mother.

62
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,260
The Ji family has come

63
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,420
to ask for the money.

64
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:12,850
Why did they come so suddenly?

65
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:14,960
Here's the plan.

66
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,390
I'll go to Zhao's place.

67
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:18,120
You handle things here for now.

68
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,430
Don't be rude.

69
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,870
Thank you for your trouble, Mother.

70
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,240
Mother, where are you going?

71
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,240
Yeah, Grandmother.

72
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,630
Madam Yao is about to arrive.

73
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,560
How can you leave?

74
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,420
That's enough.

75
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,560
This dowry list

76
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:32,720
has some issues.

77
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,900
I'll think about it some more.

78
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,240
You two

79
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,600
entertain them for now.

80
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,480
Master, what's wrong with it?

81
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,080
Wasn't this all agreed upon?

82
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,960
Is your stay at
your ancestral home going well?

83
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:48,440
Second Young Master Ji.

84
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,850
I pay my respects to you, Old Madam.

85
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,450
I haven't seen you in years.

86
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,240
You've grown into a handsome young man.

87
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:06,850
You flatter me, Old Madam.

88
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,310
We are relatives,

89
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,280
so there's no need
to beat around the bush.

90
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:12,920
I don't remember

91
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:15,240
borrowing money from your family.

92
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,960
It's been over ten years.

93
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,750
It's understandable
if you've forgotten.

94
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:26,950
Take a look at the IOU.

95
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,570
You might just remember it.

96
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,360
This was found among

97
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,480
my aunt's belongings.

98
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:35,750
[IOU]

99
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,070
Twenty years ago,

100
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:36,870
you borrowed 20,000 taels of silver

101
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:38,159
from my aunt.

102
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:40,070
With a three percent interest rate,

103
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,430
to be repaid within a year.

104
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,430
Here is your seal.

105
00:05:43,550 --> 00:05:44,670
[IOU]

106
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:50,800
What IOU?

107
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:53,070
I know nothing about it.

108
00:05:53,890 --> 00:05:55,540
But your seal is on it.

109
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:58,000
That is the strange part.

110
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:01,370
It is indeed my seal on it.

111
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:02,710
But I know absolutely

112
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:05,040
nothing about this matter.

113
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:11,600
Are you saying

114
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,720
that you refuse to acknowledge

115
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,720
this IOU?

116
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,960
The tea has gone weak.

117
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:32,830
I have

118
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:34,480
a lot of things
waiting for me at my estate.

119
00:06:33,940 --> 00:06:36,150
[Madam Yao, Yao Ping's wife]

120
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,510
I wonder how long it will take

121
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:38,310
for the Old Madam to return.

122
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:41,310
She should be here soon.

123
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:43,870
We shouldn't have kept you

124
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,390
waiting for so long.

125
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:48,659
But the family that had the incident

126
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:50,750
is the Old Madam's maternal family,

127
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:54,240
so she has to handle it herself.

128
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:57,720
She should be back any minute now.

129
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,930
Go and see

130
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,570
where the Old Madam is.

131
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,070
Yes.

132
00:07:07,350 --> 00:07:08,680
What do you mean by that?

133
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,370
Are you trying to say

134
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:11,630
that I want to dodge

135
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,230
your debt?

136
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,510
A mere 20,000 taels

137
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,720
is not something our Gu family

138
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,240
would even care about.

139
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,000
It's just that I

140
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:22,040
did not borrow this money.

141
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,240
We are relatives.

142
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,160
I won't

143
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:27,390
blame you for being disrespectful.

144
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:30,000
You should leave immediately.

145
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,420
I should head back too.

146
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:34,560
I didn't expect the dignified Gu family

147
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,720
to be like this.

148
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:38,680
Yao.

149
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:40,270
Am I wrong?

150
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,180
On this IOU,

151
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:44,800
it is clearly written in black and white.

152
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,850
The seals and fingerprints are all there.

153
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:50,430
Can your grandmother just deny it
and be done with it?

154
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,960
How can there be such logic?

155
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:56,430
Grandmother is advanced in age.

156
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,190
It is common for her to forget

157
00:07:58,190 --> 00:07:59,240
some things.

158
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,070
Yao,

159
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,680
talk to her nicely.

160
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:03,930
My grandmother

161
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:05,620
is not someone who plays dumb.

162
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,550
Right?

163
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:08,660
I have never seen this IOU.

164
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,080
Perhaps

165
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:12,100
you had it forged.

166
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,310
Forged?

167
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,480
Our Ji family,

168
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,390
for 20,000 taels,

169
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,300
needs to forge an IOU to extort you?

170
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,830
What a huge joke.

171
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,950
I did not expect

172
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,040
the family of an imperial censor

173
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,840
to have such a family tradition.

174
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:33,049
Never mind.

175
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:35,270
Since you won't admit it,

176
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,890
I will just have to

177
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:38,890
take a trip to Shuntian Prefecture.

178
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,230
Come back!

179
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,120
Yao.

180
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:42,789
Grandmother has already

181
00:08:42,789 --> 00:08:44,120
remembered this money.

182
00:08:44,550 --> 00:08:45,080
Right?

183
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,870
So you remember now?

184
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,080
Why are you acting

185
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,790
so rashly, child?

186
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,960
The matter hasn't been clarified yet.

187
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,870
Why jump straight to Shuntian Prefecture?

188
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:02,530
You are being too aggressive.

189
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,040
Old Madam,

190
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:06,550
I am not trying to be aggressive.

191
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,150
In the past,

192
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:09,840
for my aunt's sake,

193
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,550
let alone 20,000 taels,

194
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:13,270
even 40,000 or 80,000 taels,

195
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:14,870
we wouldn't have

196
00:09:14,870 --> 00:09:16,530
held it against the Gu family.

197
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,670
But now,

198
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,670
not only has my aunt passed away,

199
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,300
she was also divorced from Gu Dezhao.

200
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:25,630
Our families have nothing
to do with each other anymore.

201
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:26,390
Besides,

202
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:30,270
I haven't forgotten

203
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,150
why my aunt died.

204
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,750
I must collect

205
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,720
this debt today.

206
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,040
Old Madam,

207
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:44,610
if you have any doubts about the debt,

208
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,520
let's go to Shuntian Prefecture

209
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,750
and make it clear.

210
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:51,200
We are in-laws.

211
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:52,670
It wasn't necessary to make a scene

212
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:53,910
like this.

213
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,480
Go back and ask the Second Madam

214
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:59,270
and have her check carefully

215
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,080
to see if there is such a debt.

216
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:01,750
Yes.

217
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:11,110
Master.

218
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,970
Sorry to keep you waiting.

219
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,240
Dear.

220
00:10:28,330 --> 00:10:30,120
[Dowry Silver: 2,000 Taels]

221
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:35,370
[Dowry Silver: 2,000 Taels]

222
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,670
What's wrong, in-law?

223
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:53,360
Is there anything inappropriate?

224
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:56,060
Nothing inappropriate.

225
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:59,720
It's just my first time seeing

226
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:01,960
so little dowry money.

227
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:04,110
It just feels a bit

228
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,440
strange.

229
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,670
Nothing.

230
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,840
Let's stop here for today.

231
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,910
I'm heading back.

232
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,130
No need to see me out.

233
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:17,370
Take care.

234
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,670
Well, this...

235
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,310
What kind of talk is that?

236
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,010
Is 20,000 taels too little?

237
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:24,830
Exactly.

238
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:25,630
I don't believe

239
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:27,200
that when she married into the Yao family,

240
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,910
she had more dowry money than me.

241
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:30,360
And she still looks down on me?

242
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,390
Unbelievable.

243
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:34,670
I changed the dowry money

244
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,000
to 2,000 taels.

245
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,670
What?

246
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,550
Father!

247
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:46,510
Master,

248
00:11:46,550 --> 00:11:48,260
what are you doing?

249
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,080
What am I doing?

250
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,850
Paying debts.

251
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,480
What debts?

252
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:59,010
You don't need to know.

253
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:05,060
Why, Father?

254
00:12:05,190 --> 00:12:06,670
Why are you using my money

255
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:07,750
to pay off the debt?

256
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,510
What do you mean, your money?

257
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:12,120
It all belongs to the Gu family.

258
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,810
I'm going to tell Grandmother.

259
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,480
That's my dowry money.

260
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:19,030
I'm going to tell Grandmother right now!

261
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:25,000
If you dare bother your grandmother,

262
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,340
I'll beat you to death.

263
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,200
Will you keep the bank notes,

264
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,320
or should I deposit them
in the bank for you?

265
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,150
No need to give it to me.

266
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,910
This is the Ji family's money.

267
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,120
That won't do.

268
00:12:39,790 --> 00:12:41,430
This is Aunt's dowry money,

269
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,330
so it should be returned to you.

270
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:45,750
Then keep it for me for now.

271
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:48,200
There are too many prying eyes here.

272
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,860
I'm afraid it will attract
unwanted attention.

273
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:51,670
Alright.

274
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,490
This was a real eye-opener.

275
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:55,670
This Gu family

276
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:57,110
is rotten to the core.

277
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,750
Otherwise,

278
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,960
you should come back to Tongzhou with me.

279
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,840
With you staying here,

280
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,970
I'm really worried.

281
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,010
That won't work.

282
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,270
I have my own plans.

283
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:11,230
Don't worry.

284
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,200
Even though the people here

285
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,270
look fierce,

286
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:15,680
their little tricks

287
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:16,910
are nothing to me.

288
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:21,870
Are you still thinking
about going to Shanxi?

289
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,360
I advise you

290
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,620
to give up on that idea.

291
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,330
Look at you, here you go again.

292
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:27,120
I didn't say I'd definitely go.

293
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:28,910
I was just wondering

294
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:30,270
if that might be

295
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:31,360
a way out for me.

296
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,910
If not, I won't go.

297
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,480
My good Yao,

298
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:41,270
stop worrying about me.

299
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,870
I know what I'm doing.

300
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,080
Alright.

301
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:53,210
I've never been
able to convince you anyway.

302
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:54,370
Just one thing.

303
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:57,600
Don't let yourself be wronged.

304
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,840
I know.

305
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:04,260
[Generations of Excellence]

306
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,200
Let's go.

307
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:09,630
Lian.

308
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,080
Lian!

309
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,370
What are you doing?

310
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:19,050
That was my dowry money.

311
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:21,030
Why did it have to go to Gu Jinzhao?

312
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,860
I'm going to ask Grandmother

313
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:24,590
what is going on.

314
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:27,440
Leave us.

315
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:32,440
Haven't you embarrassed yourself enough?

316
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,850
What's the use of going?

317
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:37,250
The money has already
been returned to the Ji family.

318
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,320
Mother,

319
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,360
what should I do?

320
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,080
The Yao family has

321
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,870
three sisters-in-law above me.

322
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:45,000
On the day of the dowry display,

323
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,200
I'll definitely be laughed at.

324
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,960
I know.

325
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,480
It's fine.

326
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,000
Back then,

327
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:56,000
when the fourth branch
split from the family,

328
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,080
your Fourth Aunt

329
00:14:57,150 --> 00:14:58,510
left quite a few things

330
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,910
in the storehouse.

331
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:01,440
When the time comes,

332
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,080
I'll add a few to your dowry.

333
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:06,470
Really?

334
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,970
Are Fourth Aunt's things

335
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,360
really that good?

336
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:14,390
She was the daughter
of Tongzhou's richest man.

337
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,960
Zhao also has money.

338
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:21,910
Aren't you going to the silk shop tomorrow

339
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,810
to pick out fabric for clothes?

340
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:26,730
Go to Zhao's shop,

341
00:15:27,030 --> 00:15:29,610
and invite her along.

342
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:32,530
Let's see if she has
the nerve to ask you to pay.

343
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:34,510
All right.

344
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,870
I also want to check out
Linxia Restaurant.

345
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:37,360
Anyway,

346
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,960
I've never been there before.

347
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:40,150
Then go.

348
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,750
As an older sister,

349
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,120
it's only right that

350
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,080
she treats you to a meal

351
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,340
in her own restaurant.

352
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,630
Okay.

353
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:53,220
[Western Regions Tribute Hide]

354
00:15:53,250 --> 00:15:57,790
[Linxia Restaurant]

355
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:57,860
Boss.

356
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,390
There's no one in your restaurant.

357
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:03,890
Business is slow.

358
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:05,030
No wonder

359
00:16:05,630 --> 00:16:08,000
you charged me for a few clothes.

360
00:16:09,910 --> 00:16:11,320
Did someone book the whole place?

361
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,480
You guessed it.

362
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:13,240
Early this morning,

363
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:15,080
you sent someone to reserve a room,

364
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,670
and then a distinguished guest came,

365
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:18,030
wanting to book

366
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:18,960
the entire restaurant.

367
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,830
I told them you had a reservation,

368
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:23,020
so they only booked the second floor.

369
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:23,830
But I

370
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:25,790
didn't dare take any other guests.

371
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:27,510
What kind of distinguished guest

372
00:16:27,510 --> 00:16:29,720
books the whole place at once?

373
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,510
Third Master is here,

374
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,830
and the others are here too.

375
00:16:36,780 --> 00:16:43,350
[Linxia Restaurant]

376
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,120
Boss, please.

377
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,720
What is it?

378
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,000
So mysterious.

379
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:54,200
This dish is a bit too salty.

380
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,800
I need to freshen up.

381
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,650
You don't need to follow me.

382
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:14,010
What kind of big shot is this,

383
00:17:14,109 --> 00:17:15,640
sneaking around like this?

384
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,480
Could it be

385
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:19,440
some shady business?

386
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,599
What are you doing?

387
00:17:25,710 --> 00:17:27,720
You shouldn't go to the second floor.

388
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,580
Go back with me.

389
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:31,920
Then tell me,

390
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:33,920
who is the big shot upstairs?

391
00:17:35,150 --> 00:17:36,410
You don't need to know.

392
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,310
It won't do you any good even if you know.

393
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:39,000
Come with me.

394
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:39,930
I'm not leaving.

395
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:42,830
Why are you being so secretive?

396
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,030
Could the person upstairs

397
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:45,360
be the Emperor himself?

398
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,590
The Emperor would never come

399
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:48,120
to your shabby little shop.

400
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:49,880
Who is it?

401
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:53,720
Greetings, My Lord.

402
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,740
Are you a waitress of Linxia Restaurant?

403
00:17:59,070 --> 00:17:59,590
My Lord,

404
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:01,720
this is the boss of our shop.

405
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:03,550
The boss?

406
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:04,070
Yes.

407
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:08,370
Won't the boss come and offer a toast?

408
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:10,920
Well...

409
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:12,160
Mr. Gao,

410
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:13,720
go get

411
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:14,580
my wine cup.

412
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,030
Yes, Boss.

413
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:19,160
You are absolutely right, My Lord.

414
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,440
I was just about to go over

415
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,440
and offer a toast.

416
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,070
Hurry up.

417
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:27,920
Go back.

418
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:30,810
I'm not going back.

419
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,400
I want to offer a toast too.

420
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:32,880
What?

421
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:34,030
Are you the only one allowed

422
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:35,830
to socialize with the powerful?

423
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:38,160
You asked for this.

424
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,790
When Grandmother and Second Aunt

425
00:18:39,790 --> 00:18:40,920
ask about it later,

426
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:42,100
don't blame me.

427
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,690
Of course I won't blame you.

428
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:55,510
Come in.

429
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:12,680
Mr. Yao?

430
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:13,310
My Lord.

431
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,640
Lian?

432
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,830
W-Why are you here?

433
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,070
I... I... I...

434
00:19:20,270 --> 00:19:22,000
I... I don't know either.

435
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:24,590
I... I went the wrong way.

436
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:28,200
Why did she leave?

437
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:31,160
Lord Yao.

438
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,000
You know her?

439
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:43,510
My respects

440
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:44,960
to Third Master

441
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,030
and all lords.

442
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,020
My surname is Gu.

443
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:52,240
I am the boss of Linxia Restaurant.

444
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,200
I heard

445
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,350
you were honoring us
with your presence today,

446
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:56,980
so I came to pay my respects.

447
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:58,220
Your surname is Gu?

448
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,920
Isn't this Linxia Restaurant

449
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:02,250
the property of the Ji family in Tongzhou?

450
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:03,880
I wouldn't dare deceive you, My Lord.

451
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,160
The head of the Ji family

452
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,760
is my maternal grandmother.

453
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,200
Jiuheng.

454
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:11,590
According to what she says,

455
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,110
she works for you.

456
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,370
Aren't you her master?

457
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:16,400
I suppose so.

458
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:19,280
By the way,

459
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:20,570
why are you here?

460
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:21,680
Third Master,

461
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:24,310
my grandmother entrusted Linxia Restaurant

462
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:25,350
to my care.

463
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:27,270
So every now and then,

464
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,400
I come to check on it.

465
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:29,590
Today

466
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,160
is quite a coincidence.

467
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:34,920
Whatever you two have to say,

468
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,110
save it for later.

469
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,110
Miss Gu,

470
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:39,960
didn't you say

471
00:20:40,790 --> 00:20:42,520
you were going to offer a toast?

472
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,750
Yes.

473
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:53,060
Thank you for your care, my lords.

474
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:54,480
I would like

475
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:56,160
to offer you a toast.

476
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:04,080
I won't disturb you any longer.

477
00:21:04,110 --> 00:21:06,110
I will take my leave now.

478
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:09,510
Wait.

479
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,800
Did I say you could leave?

480
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:16,750
You just said you drop by

481
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:18,680
Linxia Restaurant every so often.

482
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:20,510
We've been here

483
00:21:20,510 --> 00:21:21,680
so many times,

484
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:22,680
but we've never seen you

485
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:24,010
come over and say hello.

486
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,440
Are you intentionally

487
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,440
avoiding us?

488
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:29,720
How could I?

489
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,510
It's just that

490
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:33,680
I was worried you were discussing

491
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,680
court secrets,

492
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:36,400
so I didn't dare to disturb you.

493
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,720
Look at this.

494
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:40,160
That sounds like a perfunctory excuse.

495
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,210
But never mind.

496
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:41,880
You,

497
00:21:42,750 --> 00:21:43,680
pour the wine.

498
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,130
A penalty drink.

499
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:50,640
Pour.

500
00:21:55,790 --> 00:21:57,090
You are right, My Lord.

501
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,300
I should...

502
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:00,460
-drink a penalty cup.
-Wait.

503
00:22:02,350 --> 00:22:03,880
One cup isn't enough.

504
00:22:04,710 --> 00:22:06,380
With so many of us here,

505
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:08,690
one cup isn't quite appropriate.

506
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:10,540
Three cups.

507
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,110
Yuanweng.

508
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:18,130
Speaking of which,

509
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:19,540
she may be the boss,

510
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:22,440
but she's just a young girl.

511
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,440
How about

512
00:22:24,350 --> 00:22:25,280
I drink with you?

513
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:30,320
Jiuheng is being tender and protective.

514
00:22:39,310 --> 00:22:41,440
I wouldn't dare trouble Third Master.

515
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,380
What you say is right, My Lord.

516
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,970
It was my negligence.

517
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:46,590
How can punishing myself
with one cup be enough?

518
00:22:46,590 --> 00:22:47,610
I should indeed

519
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:49,380
drink three cups as a penalty.

520
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:08,270
Good. How forthright.

521
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:10,880
You really have quite a spirit.

522
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:13,880
Good, good.

523
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,600
You are as good as any man.

524
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:18,380
She is the boss
of Linxia Restaurant, after all.

525
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:22,220
Then I shall excuse myself first.

526
00:23:22,550 --> 00:23:23,810
I won't spoil your fun.

527
00:23:44,270 --> 00:23:44,830
My Lady.

528
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,590
It's fine. I'm not drunk.

529
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:50,270
You may leave.

530
00:23:50,270 --> 00:23:51,400
I am fine, Mr. Gao.

531
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:52,210
Yes, My Lady.

532
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:53,910
Call me if you need anything.

533
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,200
Do you want me to

534
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:00,000
pour you a bowl of hangover soup?

535
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:01,240
It's fine.

536
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:03,150
Where is Lian?

537
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:04,920
I was just about to tell you.

538
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:05,720
Earlier, Miss Lian

539
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,790
said she had to leave
as soon as she got back,

540
00:24:06,790 --> 00:24:07,990
and has already left.

541
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:09,920
Do you know

542
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:10,890
who she ran into?

543
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:11,750
Who?

544
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,830
Yao Wenxiu's father,

545
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:15,550
Yao Ping, Lord Yao.

546
00:24:17,550 --> 00:24:18,350
Third Master.

547
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:24,380
Greetings, Third Master.

548
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:29,750
How is it?

549
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:31,640
Are you uncomfortable?

550
00:24:34,510 --> 00:24:36,640
Linxia Restaurant is elegant and quiet.

551
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,240
My mentor likes it very much,

552
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,750
and also loves to call for some

553
00:24:39,750 --> 00:24:41,240
singing girls for company.

554
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:43,040
But I don't care for such things.

555
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,070
It doesn't matter even if you do.

556
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,570
I am the boss of Linxia Restaurant.

557
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:51,760
I've seen

558
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:53,600
plenty of this sort of thing.

559
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:57,310
I shouldn't have stopped you just now.

560
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,680
With Wang Xuanfan's temper,

561
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,240
the more I try to stop him,
the more he insists.

562
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:00,830
Instead,

563
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,140
he made you drink a lot.

564
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:03,770
You don't need to explain.

565
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,400
As for me,

566
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,810
I didn't drink too much.

567
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,680
And I have a very high tolerance.

568
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:12,720
Are you

569
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:14,310
not angry at all?

570
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,160
You are a Grand Secretary.

571
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:19,590
Daily social engagements

572
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,550
are common.

573
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,510
Besides,

574
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:23,680
your coming here

575
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,070
is to support my business.

576
00:25:25,070 --> 00:25:26,310
Why would I be angry?

577
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,110
I think

578
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,640
you'd better go back early.

579
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:34,050
Don't stay out too long,

580
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,030
or else

581
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,760
it might cause more trouble.

582
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:38,410
I'll take my leave.

583
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:48,000
Third Master.

584
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,550
Miss Gu looks like

