588
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,650
You have a good eye.

589
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:06,570
Is she not angry?

590
00:26:06,900 --> 00:26:07,830
She isn't angry.

591
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,000
Jiuheng.

592
00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:18,120
Jiuheng.

593
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,680
Jiu... Jiu... Jiuheng.

594
00:26:20,590 --> 00:26:21,310
We...

595
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:23,130
We were just talking about you,

596
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:23,870
