599
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:30,270
It turns out you have someone outside.

600
00:26:31,070 --> 00:26:31,590
But

601
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,480
Miss Gu looks...

602
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,510
Yuanweng.

603
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,000
Watch your words.

604
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,440
Saying things like that

605
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:43,700
