606
00:26:43,780 --> 00:26:46,160
Besides, I still have
to get married someday.

607
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,720
Jiuheng is right.

608
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:50,210
You had too much to drink today.

609
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,950
Yes. Yes.

610
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:56,920
Look at my mouth.

611
00:26:57,920 --> 00:26:58,550
I...

612
00:26:59,110 --> 00:27:00,590
I will punish myself with a drink.

613
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:02,990
I will punish myself
with a drink, Jiuheng.

614
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:04,510
But Jiuheng,

615
00:27:04,510 --> 00:27:06,790
