623
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:20,440
It's just that

624
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,440
I haven't been able to find

625
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:23,440
a suitable match.

626
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:24,510
Is that so?

627
00:27:30,270 --> 00:27:32,720
I have a suitable match for you.

628
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:36,600
The only daughter of Grand Preceptor Xue.

629
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:37,960
Her name is

630
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:38,790
Qinglan.

631
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,200
She's 19,

632
00:27:41,110 --> 00:27:43,720
and my wife's niece.

633
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:46,720
Actually, my wife and I both think

634
00:27:46,720 --> 00:27:48,320
that you two are a good match.

635
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:49,400
What do you think?

636
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:54,550
If you both think so,

637
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:56,270
then it must be good.

638
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:57,550
I am

639
00:27:58,350 --> 00:27:59,480
