640
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,200
Good.

641
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,270
Great.

642
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:04,790
It is exactly the Indian summer now.

643
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:05,550
My wife

644
00:28:05,550 --> 00:28:07,160
is planning to hold

645
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,510
a Spring Outing.

646
00:28:09,310 --> 00:28:10,550
Firstly, to find a chance

647
00:28:10,550 --> 00:28:11,830
for you two to meet.

648
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,550
Secondly,

649
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:14,000
and most importantly,

650
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:18,330
