and maritime grain transport,

651
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:20,590
now that the national treasury is full,

652
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:22,960
it should be announced to the world.

653
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:30,070
Isn't this your idea?

654
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,980
I'll follow your arrangement, Mentor.

655
00:28:38,970 --> 00:28:42,570
[Chen Mansion]

656
00:28:45,850 --> 00:28:52,150
[Thrice Reflections Against Greed;
Ninefold Virtues in the Sound of the Qin]

657
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:48,780
Third Master, Sixth Miss is here.

658
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:54,440
Yanyun.

659
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,790
You were looking for me?

660
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:56,510
What is it?

661
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:57,890
You're here.

662
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,010
You may leave first.

663
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:06,550
What?

664
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:07,830
The Grand Secretary

665
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:09,560
