666
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,000
Well,

667
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:16,270
it's not impossible.

668
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,220
What do you think?

669
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:19,960
I want to ask you,

670
00:29:20,230 --> 00:29:22,230
