671
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,070
What kind of person

672
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:24,200
is she exactly?

673
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:27,830
Qinglan is the only daughter
of Grand Preceptor Xue.

674
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:30,070
Although she's from
a family of civil officials,

675
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:32,530
she has loved
martial arts since childhood.

676
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:33,750
Her family originally

677
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:35,200
arranged for her to marry the second son

678
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,110
of the Cui family in Baoping.

679
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,790
But before she could
marry into their family,

680
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:39,400
Young Master Cui died of illness.

681
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,860
She really has a hard life.

682
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:43,670
I have heard about this.

683
00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:45,750
What is her temperament like?

684
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:47,150
She is straightforward.

685
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,790
Although her temper isn't great,

686
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:50,190
she has a very good heart.

687
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:52,790
She's just too competitive.

688
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,720
She likes martial arts

689
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,160
and often challenges people

690
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,960
to archery and riding contests.

691
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,590
She hates it most when others

692
00:29:59,590 --> 00:30:00,750
