because she's a woman.

693
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:01,920
If someone beats her,

694
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:03,520
it actually makes her happy.

695
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:08,510
The day after tomorrow
is the Spring Outing.

696
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:10,000
Who are you planning to invite?

697
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,720
I plan to invite Wanxue to go with me,

698
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:13,060
