699
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,640
What do you think?

700
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:16,200
I was just asking.

701
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,590
You are the one inviting guests,

702
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:19,400
so you decide.

703
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:20,510
Alright.

704
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:24,400
Tomorrow at the foot of Mount Xiuyan,

705
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:25,750
[Crystal-Clear at Heart]

706
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:26,060
there will be a Spring Outing.

707
00:30:26,350 --> 00:30:27,550
Eldest Miss Xue

708
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:28,740
and the wife of the Grand Secretary

709
00:30:28,740 --> 00:30:29,680
are co-hosting it.

710
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:32,400
They invited families of all
the high-ranking officials in the capital.

711
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,560
Wenxiu

712
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:34,010
[For Miss Gu's Esteemed Perusal]

713
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:35,110
