717
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:46,350
This invitation is

718
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,400
[For Miss Gu's Esteemed Perusal]

719
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:47,750
really exquisite.

720
00:30:49,350 --> 00:30:50,030
Zhao,

721
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:52,240
I heard you can also ride horses.

722
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,270
Why don't you

723
00:30:53,350 --> 00:30:54,200
take Zhao

724
00:30:54,280 --> 00:30:54,900
and Lan

725
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:56,240
out to play?

726
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:57,870
Normally,

727
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,000
they wouldn't have such an opportunity

728
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:01,060
to meet powerful and wealthy people.

729
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:02,510
How can I do that?

730
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:05,860
Wenxiu only invited me.

731
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:08,130
