743
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:39,950
[Crystal-Clear at Heart]

744
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:35,540
Okay.

745
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,240
Mother.

746
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:51,420
[Spring Outing]

747
00:31:53,490 --> 00:31:55,730
[Outing]

748
00:31:56,650 --> 00:31:58,350
You look really pretty today.

749
00:31:58,510 --> 00:31:59,160
Really?

750
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,860
My nanny altered it for me.

751
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,360
You're dressed quite plainly, though.

752
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:05,160
Yeah, I was wondering

753
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,110
why today

754
00:32:06,110 --> 00:32:07,920
everyone is dressed so brightly.

755
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,350
It makes me look unprepared.

756
00:32:09,350 --> 00:32:11,200
It's because this is a rare opportunity.

757
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,350
There are many rules in the capital.

758
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:13,590
When female family members socialize,

759
00:32:13,590 --> 00:32:15,350
it's usually just visiting
each other's homes.

760
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,430
But when visiting others,

761
00:32:16,430 --> 00:32:18,310
it's inevitable to meet older relatives,

762
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:19,160
which makes things restricted

763
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:20,090
and not much fun.

764
00:32:20,550 --> 00:32:21,830
With an event like the Spring Outing,

765
00:32:21,830 --> 00:32:22,640
where there are no elders

766
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,160
and you can play freely,

767
00:32:24,270 --> 00:32:26,200
everyone goes all out dressing up.

768
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:29,070
Wenxiu!

769
00:32:32,130 --> 00:32:34,170
[Yao Wenxiu, son of Yao Ping]

770
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:34,640
Lian.

771
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:42,170
Wenxiu,

772
00:32:42,270 --> 00:32:43,400
I want to go horseback riding.

773
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,790
Let's go pick a horse over there.

774
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:45,400
Okay.

775
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,550
The stables have many horses.

776
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:49,150
We can go pick some together.

777
00:32:51,320 --> 00:32:52,890
I don't know how to ride,

778
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:54,380
so I won't go.

779
00:32:54,750 --> 00:32:56,010
You don't have to ride.

780
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:57,470
We can just go take a look.

781
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:59,480
Otherwise, if you stay here alone,

782
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:00,480
we'd be worried.

783
00:33:02,560 --> 00:33:03,830
Well... alright.

784
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,000
You...

785
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:08,920
Okay.

786
00:33:10,030 --> 00:33:10,560
Let's go.

787
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:16,890
Don't be afraid.

788
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,920
Horses are intelligent creatures.

789
00:33:20,270 --> 00:33:21,510
Thank you, Young Master Yao.

790
00:33:21,510 --> 00:33:23,240
Why are you calling me so distantly?

791
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,640
Just call me Wenxiu.

792
00:33:27,550 --> 00:33:28,880
Yes, Wenxiu.

793
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,000
What's wrong?

794
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,480
Why didn't you pick a horse just now?

795
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:39,590
When I was young,

796
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:41,190
I fell off a horse.

797
00:33:41,310 --> 00:33:43,770
I haven't dared to
get close to horses since.

798
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,550
A horse is coming over.

799
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:58,110
This horse seems to know you.

800
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:01,150
Yeah, sure seems like it.

801
00:34:02,350 --> 00:34:03,350
Do you know me?

802
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,280
I don't know

803
00:34:06,310 --> 00:34:07,680
where it came from.

804
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,510
Xuanqing

805
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:15,920
is here too.

806
00:34:18,190 --> 00:34:19,250
Young Master Chen?

807
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,000
Why is he here?

808
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:23,980
I heard he joined the Hanlin Academy.

809
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,780
Why are you blushing?

810
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,230
I...

811
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,510
I'm engaged to him.

812
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,190
Congratulations.

813
00:34:33,190 --> 00:34:34,520
When did it happen?

814
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,250
Before the metropolitan examination.

815
00:34:36,250 --> 00:34:37,820
You are really lucky.

816
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:40,460
He placed third
in the imperial examination.

817
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:42,090
Stop making fun of me.

818
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,480
He's here.

819
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:53,770
Miss Gu.

820
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,060
Young Master Chen.

821
00:34:58,060 --> 00:34:58,660
Miss Yu.

822
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,670
Xuanqing.

823
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:06,060
Young Master Chen.

824
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:07,340
Hope you've been well.

825
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:09,300
Take your time.

826
00:35:09,510 --> 00:35:11,510
I can't wait to go horseback riding.

827
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:20,920
I'm leaving.

828
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:21,680
Let's go.

829
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:24,320
Hyah!

830
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,000
Hyah!

831
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:31,010
A lot of people are practicing.

832
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:36,230
[Outing]

833
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:32,320
Wenxiu,

834
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:33,300
let's play too.

835
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:35,180
I'm going to the field,

836
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,370
but you shouldn't go.

837
00:35:36,630 --> 00:35:37,140
[Outing]

838
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:38,890
As a girl,

839
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,280
if you fall,

840
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:42,620
you'll make a fool of yourself in public.

841
00:35:43,550 --> 00:35:44,360
Yao!

842
00:35:45,230 --> 00:35:45,760
Zan?

843
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:46,330
Let's go,

844
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,460
get some practice.

845
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,280
Let's go.

846
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:48,810
Let's go.

847
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:05,550
I'm warning you.

848
00:36:05,550 --> 00:36:07,100
Stay away from Wenxiu.

849
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,760
If you act

850
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:09,480
