856
00:36:15,550 --> 00:36:17,810
Who gave you the right to call him Wenxiu?

857
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:19,510
What's wrong?

858
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,380
Look at you.

859
00:36:28,550 --> 00:36:29,810
You're doing it again.

860
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:31,000
Doing what?

861
00:36:31,020 --> 00:36:32,600
She didn't even say anything.

862
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:33,600
Don't bully her.

863
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:35,360
Me bullying her?

864
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,760
She's obviously pretending

865
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:37,840
to be pitiful

866
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:38,880
to seduce you.

867
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,760
When did I ever seduce him?

868
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,080
It was obviously him...

869
00:36:42,080 --> 00:36:43,030
Alright, alright.

870
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:43,830
Stop arguing.

871
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:45,720
You...

872
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:48,550
Wenxiu.

873
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,560
In previous years,

874
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:05,000
we wouldn't have had so much money

875
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,930
to hold such a grand Spring Outing.

876
00:37:07,110 --> 00:37:08,200
The imperial court

877
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,710
is wealthy now.

878
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:10,760
Yes.

879
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:13,350
This is all thanks to Xuanweng

880
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,390
and the new tax policy.

881
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:18,510
I heard the rules for today’s

882
00:37:18,510 --> 00:37:20,030
archery contest
have been changed as well.

883
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:22,120
Men and women are competing together.

884
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:23,920
Isn't this a bit inappropriate?

885
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:26,160
What's inappropriate about it?

886
00:37:27,450 --> 00:37:30,560
[Xue Qinglan, daughter
of Grand Preceptor Xue]

887
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,010
Riding and shooting

888
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:31,840
rely on horsemanship and accuracy.

889
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:33,670
It has nothing to do
with physical strength or endurance.

890
00:37:33,670 --> 00:37:36,000
Why can't men and women compete together?

891
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,920
You are right, Miss.

892
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,880
I was biased.

893
00:37:45,190 --> 00:37:47,050
You changed your tune quite fast.

894
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,730
Greetings, Uncle.

895
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,400
Aunt.

896
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,030
How is your father?

897
00:37:58,670 --> 00:38:00,190
My father had too much
to drink again today.

898
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:01,240
He was afraid you'd scold him,

899
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:02,640
so he didn't dare to come.

900
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,840
The wind passing through the forest

901
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,110
has actually blown away the heaviness

902
00:38:09,110 --> 00:38:10,090
in my heart.

903
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,030
Since my mother passed away,

904
00:38:12,030 --> 00:38:12,590
I haven't had

905
00:38:12,590 --> 00:38:14,050
such a relaxing moment.

906
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:16,480
Only by knowing the vastness of the world,

907
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,940
do old sorrows feel light.

908
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:19,510
Indeed.

909
00:38:19,670 --> 00:38:21,510
Since the green mountains are so charming,

910
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:22,070
why should I

911
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:24,130
still cling to the storms of the past?

912
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:28,460
Are you going that way?

913
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:34,760
Make way!

914
00:38:41,090 --> 00:38:42,100
Slow down!

915
00:38:45,630 --> 00:38:46,690
What are you doing?

916
00:39:27,830 --> 00:39:29,360
I know you're in a hurry,

917
00:39:29,510 --> 00:39:31,300
but if you always think about

918
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:33,190
throwing me off and walking by yourself,

919
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:34,360
that's your fault.

920
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,210
You know?

921
00:39:35,670 --> 00:39:36,320
If you do this

922
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:37,350
again next time,

923
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,530
I'll have to whip you again.

924
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:41,410
Alright,

925
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:41,960
go.

926
00:39:55,710 --> 00:39:56,920
Chen Yanyun?

927
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:00,820
Who is this woman?

928
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:04,070
Look, look, look.

929
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:04,550
So...

930
00:40:04,710 --> 00:40:05,670
So this horse

931
00:40:05,670 --> 00:40:07,600
came here for a marriage match too.

932
00:40:09,070 --> 00:40:10,230
And it just so happens to be the same day

933
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,030
as Jiuheng's.

934
00:40:12,630 --> 00:40:13,540
Jiuheng,

935
00:40:13,590 --> 00:40:15,000
isn't that black horse

936
00:40:15,190 --> 00:40:16,250
yours?

937
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,710
Yes, Mentor.

938
00:40:20,030 --> 00:40:21,030
That brown

939
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:22,690
Yuhuacong steed is also mine.

940
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:24,320
Somehow,

941
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:26,050
Miss Gu ended up riding it.

942
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:37,530
Isn't she

943
00:40:37,630 --> 00:40:39,440
the lady boss of Linxia Restaurant?

944
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:40,150
Yes.

945
00:40:40,670 --> 00:40:41,320
Jiuheng,

946
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,400
your surbordinate

947
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,130
was so well-behaved last time.

948
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,320
Why didn't she

949
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:46,440
greet you today?

950
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:48,500
That's just her temper.

951
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:50,510
Probably the horse annoyed her,

952
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:51,960
so she got angry.

953
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:54,320
You are afraid of her getting angry?

954
00:40:54,550 --> 00:40:55,760
Are you the master,

955
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:57,110
or is she the master?

956
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,320
I'm so mad!

957
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:08,160
The more I think about it,
the angrier I get.

958
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:10,050
I told you to find noble ladies,

959
00:41:10,070 --> 00:41:11,850
but I didn't tell you to go so early.

960
00:41:11,850 --> 00:41:13,630
You just went to Tongzhou
the day before yesterday,

961
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:15,960
and today you are
discussing marriage here.

962
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,640
Men.

963
00:41:19,590 --> 00:41:20,320
Zhao.

964
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:22,610
Didn't you go horseback riding?

965
00:41:22,610 --> 00:41:23,570
Why are you back?

966
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:26,230
That horse is no good.

967
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,700
It has a fierce temper.

968
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:30,840
I'm a little tired,

969
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:32,240
and want to go back first.

970
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,960
I just wanted to let you know.

971
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:35,700
You want to go back now?

972
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,000
Then I'll go back too.

973
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:38,710
Let's go.

974
00:41:42,070 --> 00:41:43,280
You ride a horse well.

975
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,350
What's your name?

976
00:41:45,630 --> 00:41:46,550
The archery contest is about to begin.

977
00:41:46,550 --> 00:41:47,950
Let's compete together.

978
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:48,960
No need.

979
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:50,440
Why not?

980
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,550
Looking at you,

981
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:53,710
you don't seem like the type

982
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:55,550
who is strictly controlled by your family.

983
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:57,010
Are you afraid to compete?

984
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:58,150
Afraid of losing?

985
00:41:58,590 --> 00:41:59,720
I am perfectly fine.

986
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:02,030
Why would I go down
there and get all sweaty,

987
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,780
just to be pointed at?

988
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:05,130
What's in it for me?

989
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,140
For the prizes!

990
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:07,920
Among today's prizes,

991
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:08,920
there's a Ferghana horse

992
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:09,850
and a fine sword.

993
00:42:10,150 --> 00:42:12,150
They're both incredibly valuable.

994
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,150
So what if they're valuable?

995
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,320
I don't care about them.

996
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,000
Don't go.

997
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:17,840
I'm not feeling well.

998
00:42:18,150 --> 00:42:20,360
I don't think you're physically unwell.

999
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,920
You have something
on your mind, don't you?

1000
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,180
But it doesn't matter.

1001
00:42:23,550 --> 00:42:25,680
Go down, ride a bit, shoot a few arrows,

1002
00:42:26,590 --> 00:42:27,920
and you'll feel better.

1003
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:30,150
Thanks for the suggestion.

1004
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:31,080
Maybe next time.

1005
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:33,110
It's rare for me to see a woman

1006
00:42:33,110 --> 00:42:34,550
whose riding skills are as good as mine.

1007
00:42:34,550 --> 00:42:36,410
I bet your archery is just as good.

1008
00:42:36,840 --> 00:42:37,440
Let's go down

1009
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,700
and have a match later.

1010
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,590
I told you, no need.

1011
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,930
It's not just for the competition.

1012
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:47,000
The guests today
are all families of civil officials.

1013
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:48,320
Civil officials only care
for poetry and refinement,

1014
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:49,440
and are not good at riding and archery.

1015
00:42:49,440 --> 00:42:50,440
Since they don't like it,

1016
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:52,440
they naturally won't
let their daughters learn it.

1017
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,800
I specially organized

1018
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:55,930
this mixed-gender competition today

1019
00:42:56,030 --> 00:42:56,590
just to show

1020
00:42:56,590 --> 00:42:58,070
those men

1021
00:42:58,590 --> 00:43:00,550
that we women riding and shooting

1022
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:01,840
are just as capable.

1023
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:04,620
If you ask me,

1024
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:05,670
competing

1025
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:07,510
just for prizes is boring.

1026
00:43:08,190 --> 00:43:09,850
Why don't we change the prizes

1027
00:43:10,070 --> 00:43:10,920
into cash?

1028
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,110
Let's put all the cash

1029
00:43:13,110 --> 00:43:14,190
into a pool,

1030
00:43:14,590 --> 00:43:17,070
and donate it all
to Hall of Benevolence after the match.

1031
00:43:17,070 --> 00:43:18,130
Whoever wins

1032
00:43:18,360 --> 00:43:20,290
will have it donated in their name.

1033
00:43:21,070 --> 00:43:22,230
That's a good idea.

1034
00:43:22,760 --> 00:43:23,670
This way,

1035
00:43:23,670 --> 00:43:25,110
persuading those men

1036
00:43:25,110 --> 00:43:26,230
will be justified.

1037
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:28,510
I'll use your method.

1038
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:29,910
Would you like to join me?

1039
00:43:30,550 --> 00:43:31,280
Of course.

1040
00:43:31,670 --> 00:43:32,070
Good.

1041
00:43:32,320 --> 00:43:34,120
I'll take you to change clothes.

1042
00:43:34,400 --> 00:43:35,110
-Let’s go.
-Let’s go.

1043
00:43:35,110 --> 00:43:35,640
Let's go.

1044
00:43:47,780 --> 00:43:49,420
You really invited her here.

1045
00:43:49,670 --> 00:43:50,280
Of course.

1046
00:43:50,510 --> 00:43:51,590
When I step in myself,

1047
00:43:51,590 --> 00:43:52,630
how could I fail?

1048
00:43:54,920 --> 00:43:56,570
Are you going to play today?

1049
00:43:56,710 --> 00:43:57,280
Yes.

1050
00:43:57,480 --> 00:43:58,440
Qinglan asked me

1051
00:43:58,440 --> 00:43:59,190
to practice half a month ago.

1052
00:43:59,190 --> 00:44:00,150
If I don don't play,

1053
00:44:00,150 --> 00:44:01,590
she won't let me off.

1054
00:44:01,840 --> 00:44:02,440
All right.

1055
00:44:02,550 --> 00:44:03,680
You practice first.

1056
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:04,550
I'll go over there

1057
00:44:04,550 --> 00:44:05,750
and invite those men.

1058
00:44:06,110 --> 00:44:07,480
Remember to invite
my third brother, Yanyun.

1059
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:08,480
Want to see him lose to me?

1060
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:09,070
Yes.

1061
00:44:15,400 --> 00:44:16,630
She always thought Yanyun

1062
00:44:16,630 --> 00:44:17,920
is a weak scholar

1063
00:44:17,920 --> 00:44:19,060
who does no physical labor.

1064
00:44:19,060 --> 00:44:19,920
Wait and see how Yanyun

1065
00:44:19,920 --> 00:44:21,120
surprises her later.

1066
00:44:21,840 --> 00:44:23,170
From what I saw earlier,

1067
00:44:23,190 --> 00:44:25,400
something felt rather odd between

1068
00:44:25,590 --> 00:44:27,140
Third Master and Miss Xue.

1069
00:44:27,440 --> 00:44:28,480
What could be odd?

1070
00:44:28,480 --> 00:44:29,710
Madam Fu played matchmaker

1071
00:44:29,710 --> 00:44:31,460
to set Yanyun and Qinglan up.

1072
00:44:31,800 --> 00:44:32,590
Actually,

1073
00:44:32,820 --> 00:44:34,480
I think they are quite a match.

1074
00:44:34,480 --> 00:44:35,550
Yanyun is sly,

1075
00:44:35,670 --> 00:44:37,600
and Qinglan is like a firecracker.

1076
00:44:38,030 --> 00:44:39,150
Indeed sly.

1077
00:44:51,780 --> 00:44:55,300
[A Splendid Match]
